<h1>API Key Signup</h1>

<p>Your API key for <strong><%= @user.email %></strong> is:</p>
<code class="signup-key"><%= @user.api_key %></code>

<p>You can start using this key to make Web service requests. Simply pass your key in the URL when making a Web request. Here's an example:</p>
<pre><%= link_to("http://api.data.gov/api/nrel/alt-fuel-stations/v1/nearest.json?<strong>api_key=#{@user.api_key}</strong><br />&location=1617+Cole+Blvd+80401".html_safe, "/api/nrel/alt-fuel-stations/v1/nearest.json?api_key=#{@user.api_key}&location=1617+Cole+Blvd+80401") %></pre>

